short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Custom homepage that grabs images off r/moescape for a certain aesthetic when a new page is opened.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A new tab override that grabs an image off of reddit's API to display as a wallpaper.

Has a google search functionality + a link to the image source with the use of a reddit icon.

It greets users with a clock and a short message picked depending on the time.

It is targeted for users that want to display a nicer image on their homepage compared to just the regular chrome new tab.
